    <Placemark>
      <name>7705305777</name>
      <description>041356Z MAY 26  NAVAREA IV 413/26.  CARIBBEAN SEA.  TRINIDAD AND TOBAGO.  1. BRIGAND HILL LIGHT 10-29.61N 061-04.20W     CHANGED TO FL (5) W 20 SEC 217 METERS 17 MILES.  2. CANCEL NAVAREA IV 406/26.  032016Z MAY 26  NAVAREA IV 412/26.  1. NORTH AMERICAN ICE SERVICE (NAIS)     ICEBERG BULLETIN 040001Z MAY.  2. WARNING! THE INTERNATIONAL ICE PATROL     IS EXPERIENCING REDUCED ICEBERG     RECONNAISSANCE. ALL ICEBERG LIMITS     REPORTED BELOW ARE ESTIMATED.     PLEASE NAVIGATE WITH CAUTION.  3. ICEB</description>
